(650, 1, '2018-04-20 11:13:08', '2018-04-20 11:13:08', '<p>[vc_row full_width="stretch_row_content_no_spaces"][vc_column][rev_slider alias="homepage"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1524222777229{margin-top: 25px !important;padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 class="no-margin-top" style="font-size: 16px;">We ensure sustained behavior change and drive successfull performance.</h3>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=".vc_custom_1460521049287{margin-bottom: 20px !important;}"][vc_column width="1/3"][imagebox button_text="Learn more" title="What we Offer" image="75" link="#"]Effective Solutions with  proven output, expert perspective to help you meet your exact development needs , achieved after burning gallons of midnight oil to brainstorm and debate on what exactly needs to be done to help our Youngsters to Astutely Position their Natural Abilities.[/imagebox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][imagebox button_text="Learn more" title="A Focus on WIN-WIN Training" image="76" link="#"]Irony of fulfilling an expectation of another person is that, the beneficiary expects that his/her second expectation also would get fulfilled by the person who fulfilled the first expectation.We have re-worked on our Programs multiple times, to ensure that our Youngsters get the best of the inputs.[/imagebox][/vc_column][vc_column width="1/3"][imagebox button_text="Learn more" title="Successful Entrepreneurs" image="77" link="#"]Mere possession of academic knowledge hardly supports a successful journey in either Employment or Entrepreneurship.We are committed to provide world class inputs to the budding entrepreneurs so that they are totally empowered to become successful entrepreneurs.[/imagebox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" equal_height="yes" css=".vc_custom_1523972974006{padding-top: 25px !important;background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}"][vc_column css_animation="fadeIn" el_id="acid" el_class="accls"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<div class="title-button">\r\n<h3 class="style1"><i class="fa fa-2x fa-line-chart"></i>Message from the Chairman and Managing Director</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<div class="cont">\r\n<p>Organizations which have strong and compelling reasons for coming into existence are more likely to overcome the initial turbulence, and achieve its objectives. Organizations achieve greatness if the compelling reasons serve as an answer to the problems the society at large is facing.</div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1523946695061{background-color: #f7f7f7 !important;}" el_id="reasid" el_class="reascls"][vc_column css_animation="slideInLeft" width="2/3"][vc_tta_accordion active_section="1" el_id="reasonid" el_class="reasoncls"][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-users" add_icon="true" title="What are our compelling reasons?" tab_id="1523946570950-b93639b5-e394"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<p>We look at our Country as a Country of Youngsters. Over 65% of Indians are under 35 years, and almost 50% of Indians are below age of 25 years. This fact, read with another fact that we are the World’s Second Largest Populated Country, presents to us a wonderful opportunity for us to be the Power House that we deserve to be. We visualize the younger population of our Country to be the real torch bearers for a Powerful, Vibrant India.</p>\r\n<p>However, for us to reach where we deserve to be, the only way is to harness the efforts of our Youngsters, and help them match potential to performance. Obviously, there is a long way to go, and a lot to do.</p>\r\n<p>Our focus would be to eradicate the bane of Unemployment and Underemployment that has started showing its ugly face. My Team is committed to enhance the Effectiveness Quotient of our Youngsters in their pursuit of a successful corporate career.<br />\r\n[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-handshake-o" add_icon="true" title="This is our first compelling reason." tab_id="1523946571019-5d74ee1d-2400"][vc_column_text]We believe that our Country needs more job creators than at present. It would do a world of good to our would-be entrepreneurs, if they were given the right type of inputs and mentoring, so that the percentage of success stories of start-ups go up.</p>\r\n<p>We are committed to provide world class inputs to the budding entrepreneurs so that they are totally empowered to become successful entrepreneurs. Our unique Entrepreneurship Experiential Learning Program provides invaluable practical experience in en[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-thumbs-o-up" add_icon="true" title="This is our second compelling reason." tab_id="1523949135607-74041eda-9a49"][vc_column_text]We all know that India is a Country of Villages. Our Villages are gifted with innumerable natural resources. Mother Nature has blessed our Villages with all her kindness. We see it as an irony that our rural youth are turning to Cities for earning a living, mostly in mundane chores.</p>\r\n<p>We want to facilitate meaningful employment and entrepreneurial opportunities at the village level. We are really captured by the multitude of problems this would solve. We have instituted concepts of ’LIFE’, and ‘A Rendezvous with Nature’ to restore the past glory of our Villages.[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-certificate" add_icon="true" title="This is our third compelling reason." tab_id="1523950832394-df6e3e09-240a"][vc_column_text]We are unconditionally committed to our compelling reasons.</p>\r\n<p>Most people would recollect being told when they were young, that ‘The Future of the Country belongs to its Youngsters’. That Statement was never more truthful, than at present.</p>\r\n<p>We have burnt gallons of midnight oil to brainstorm and debate on what exactly needs to be done to help our Youngsters to Astutely Position their Natural Abilities. We have re-worked on our Programs multiple times, to ensure that our Youngsters get the best of the inputs. We have priced our Products in a way that creates a WIN-WIN experience for everyone.</p>\r\n<p>We commit ourselves to perform every act, in total conformity to Legal and Moral compliance. We are committed to demonstrate every quality that we like to see in our Youngsters – Total Compliance to Law, Highest Moral and Ethical Standards, an effort that matches Potential, and a genuine concern for People Development. After all, a Dream to create meaningful Employment Opportunities to 100000 Youngsters, and help create 10000 Entrepreneurs, all in a span of three years, will happen only if there were to be stringent processes towards Strategy and Culture.</p>\r\n<p>We welcome readers to connect with me through my mail id, on how you want to be a part of the exciting journey that we have embarked on. I will be happy to discuss possibilities.</p>\r\n<p>Together, let us build a Vibrant India.</p>\r\n<p>Manjunath</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-envelope" style="margin-right: 5px;"></i><a href="mailto:manjunath@allevareacademy.com">manjunath@allevareacademy.com</a>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_accordion][/vc_column][vc_column css_animation="slideInRight" width="1/3" el_id="pcid" el_class="pccls"][vc_single_image image="450" img_size="full" el_id="penid" el_class="epencls"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1460520975088{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;background-color: #f1f2f8 !important;}"][vc_column css_animation="bounceInRight"][vc_empty_space height="30px"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<div class="title-button">\r\n<h3 class="style1"><i class="fa fa-2x fa-line-chart"></i>What we Offer to:</h3>\r\n<p><a class="button sm border" href="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/college">View all programs</a></div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="30px"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-graduation-cap" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-pie-chart" title="College Students/Unemployed Graduates" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/college/"]After completing formal education, it is the dream of every youngster[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-laptop" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-line-chart" title="Organizations in need of Entry Level Positions " link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/entry-level/"]Many Organizations hire employees at entry level, in large numbers.[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-star" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-line-chart" title="Franchise Seekers" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/franchise-seekers/"]How successful your business is depends on how careful you are during the selection process[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-smile-o" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-area-chart" title="Parents of College Students/Unemployed Graduates" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/parents/"]Congratulations to you, for passing yet another milestone in your life,[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-briefcase" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-bank" title="Organizations in need of beneficial Interns." link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/interns/"]We provide organizations with workaholic &amp; skilled interns.[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-user-circle-o" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-bank" title="Service Volunteers" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/service-volunteers/"]Volunteering is a life changing experience ,which will not only show you the true face of society,[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-university" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-bar-chart-o" title="Colleges/Institutions" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/institutions/"]We help Institutions by providing aplomb trainings to students, Focusing on improving their Knowledge of the self &amp; sector of interest,[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-hand-peace-o" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-bank" title="Recruitment Organizations" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/recruitment/"]We help you in recruiting top talents ,highly skilled and trained employees to bring down your training[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-money" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-line-chart" title="Investors" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/investors/"]Finding the best place to invest is a challenge that we help you fulfill,[/iconbox][vc_empty_space height="30px"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][vc_row_inner el_id="seprowid" el_class="seprowcls"][vc_column_inner el_class="elecls" width="1/3" el_id="eleid"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][iconbox icon_fontawesome="fa fa-area-chart" tag="h4" text="Learn more" icon="fa-line-chart" title="Landowners-Rural Entrepreneurship" link="http://localhost/allevare/training-programs/landowners/"]We help you find the best way to utilise your property and make,[/iconbox][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" parallax="content-moving" parallax_image="79" el_class="bg-scheme2" css=".vc_custom_1524063512202{padding-top: 165px !important;padding-bottom: 165px !important;background-position: center;background-repeat: no-repeat !important;background-size: cover !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 class="no-margin-top" style="text-align: center; line-height: 1.3;"><span style="color: #ffffff;">It is said that Numbers tell a Story. Let us take a look at the Numbers relating to people in India.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css=".vc_custom_1523975764025{padding-top: 50px !important;padding-bottom: 100px !important;background-color: #f9f9f9 !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text css_animation="slideInLeft" css=".vc_custom_1523976584342{margin-bottom: 25px !important;}"]</h3>\r\n<div class="title-button">\r\n<h3 class="style1"><i class="fa fa-2x fa-line-chart"></i>Some worth knowing Facts</h3>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_tta_tour color="sky" tab_position="right" active_section="1" css_animation="fadeIn" no_fill_content_area="true" el_id="factid" el_class="factcls"][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-bar-chart" add_icon="true" title="Fact 1" tab_id="1523971859776-5059f06d-fd31"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Age Facts</h3>\r\n<div class="list1">\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Birth Rate in our Country, which already has a population of over 1.34 Billion, is growing at literally One Child Birth every Second.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Almost 50% of Indians are below the age of 24 years.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>More than 65% of the population is below 35 years.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>People above 55 years of age, hardly constitute 14% of the Population.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Current average age of Indian is 27 years.</div>\r\n<div class="space">All these clearly indicate that our Country is blessed with a very large number of younger and middle aged population. Becoming a Super Power is within handshaking distance from us.</div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-graduation-cap" add_icon="true" title="Fact 2" tab_id="1523971859927-6dde2b54-fd38"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Educational Facts</h3>\r\n<div class="list1">\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Our Country has over 7500 Engineering Colleges, over 6500 Management Colleges, and over 100000 Degree/Diploma Colleges.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Almost 40 Million Students get graduated in different Courses, each year.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Many Surveys have established that less than 15% of the above population are employable, purely on basis of academic qualification.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Nearly 47% of India’s Population (Below 29 years and excluding the Under 5 year kids), are available for Employment.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Nearly 1 out of 4 Employees are actually under employed.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Little over 3 Lakh Jobs are created in 2016-17, in the Organized Sector. A significant majority of them are Contractual Jobs.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Job to Job Seeker Ratio is more than 1:100.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>In spite of these scary statistics, the first year attrition is almost 20%.</div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-question" add_icon="true" title="Fact 3" tab_id="1523974662353-e015a05f-7cfc"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">Decision Making Facts</h3>\r\n<div class="list1">\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Mere Academic Qualification hardly supports Job Selection.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>Focus on mere ‘Skilling’ may not significantly improve the possibility of getting a Job. The focus should be ‘Beyond Skilling’.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>A large population of our Youngsters lack the right Direction and Focus.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>There has to be a consistent ‘NURTURING’ the young minds, so that their ‘Thinking’ is on Positive Contribution.</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i>We need to significantly focus on Job Creation, by encouraging Entrepreurship, and provide the right Mentoring to the Entrepreneurs.</div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section i_icon_fontawesome="fa fa-trophy" add_icon="true" title="Fact 4" tab_id="1523975082303-d6bd2c43-7037"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 style="text-align: center;">5 critical parameters to succeed in Life</h3>\r\n<div class="list1">\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i><strong>KNOWLEDGE </strong>(of self as well as the Sector one would like to get involved with),</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i><strong>SKILLS</strong> (which separates them from the ordinary),</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i><strong>COMPETENCY</strong> (which gives them the Confidence and Belief),</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i><strong>HABITS</strong> (which leads them to Perfection) and</p>\r\n<p><i class="fa fa-hand-o-right"></i><strong>MINDSET</strong> (which helps them overcome barriers).</div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tour][vc_column_text css_animation="slideInRight" css=".vc_custom_1523976594644{margin-bottom: 25px !important;}" el_id="fendid" el_class="fendcls"]</p>\r\n<div class="fctend">\r\n<p>Unfortunately, under the current situation, many students who pass out of their academic course do not possess good control over any of the 5 parameters. Not surprisingly, a large majority of them struggle in either getting a right job, or in succeeding in their employment career. Similar is the fate in the field of Entrepreneurship.</p>\r\n<p>Allevare Academy Private Limited is committed to NURTURE Young Population of our Country in being the ‘Catalysts of Change’ that our Country need, in our quest of becoming The Super Power.</p>\r\n<p>By the way, Allevare means NURTURE.</div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation="slideInLeft" css=".vc_custom_1524147275068{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 40px !important;}" el_id="newsid" el_class="newscls"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<div class="title-button">\r\n<h3 class="style1"><i class="fa fa-2x fa-newspaper-o"></i>Our Blogs</h3>\r\n<p><a class="button sm border" href="http://localhost/allevare/news/">View all articles</a></div>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="30px"][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner width="2/3"][posts grid_columns="2" limit="2" offset="0" hide_content="yes" content_length="40" hide_readmore="yes"][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/3"][posts grid_columns="1" limit="4" offset="2" hide_content="yes" content_length="40" hide_readmore="yes"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row full_width="stretch_row" css_animation="fadeIn" css=".vc_custom_1524063297508{padding-top: 40px !important;background: #000000 url(http://localhost/allevare/wp-content/uploads/2018/04/9.png?id=524) !important;}" el_id="missid" el_class="misscls"][vc_column][vc_row_inner][vc_column_inner el_class="mvvcls" width="1/2" el_id="mvvid"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 class="style2 bg-dark" style="color: #ffffff;">Our Mission,Vision &amp; Values</h3>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="15px"][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><span style="color: #d8e7ef;"><i class="fa fa-rocket"></i>Mission</span></h4>\r\n<p><span style="color: white;">To Nurture Young minds and create employment opportunity, in a great platform to showcase their potential and succeed</span></p>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><span style="color: #d8e7ef;"><i class="fa fa-eye"></i>Vision</span></h4>\r\n<p><span style="color: white;">To design programs and materials to be quickly and economically adaptable for any audience, without sacrificing the quality or integrity of the training solution.</span>[/vc_column_text][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h4 style="font-size: 16px; margin-bottom: 10px;"><span style="color: #d8e7ef;"><i class="fa fa-handshake-o"></i>Values</span></h4>\r\n<p><span style="color: white;">We take a broader, more holistic view of all of the factors that influence the desired changes, and help you develop and execute the strategies and processes needed to implement these changes and ensure lasting results.</span>[/vc_column_text][/vc_column_inner][vc_column_inner width="1/2"][vc_empty_space height="100px"][vc_single_image image="468" img_size="full" el_id="mvvimgid" el_class="mvvimgcls"][/vc_column_inner][/vc_row_inner][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css_animation="slideInRight" css=".vc_custom_1524147264548{padding-top: 40px !important;padding-bottom: 60px !important;}"][vc_column][vc_column_text]</p>\r\n<h3 class="style1"><i class="fa fa-2x fa-commenting"></i>what our customers have to say about us</h3>\r\n<p>[/vc_column_text][vc_empty_space height="50px"][elements_carousel items="2" autoplay="no" controls="navigation,rewind-navigation" autoplay_speed="5000" slide_speed="200" pagination_speed="200" rewind_speed="200" tablet_items="2" mobile_items="1"][testimonial name="Vishal KVS" image="118" subtitle="CEO" company="Unified" link="#"]Your commitment, passion, and delivery were really amazing. We had a great start and the speed as well as intensity with which we rolled out globally over 3 years was unbelievable.[/testimonial][testimonial name="Miranda" image="119" subtitle="CEO" company="Financial" link="#"]We want to share the results of our Richardson seminar. It was a HUGE success! Rating a 5.73 on a scale of 6.0 - the highest rating a training program has gotten here.[/testimonial][testimonial name="Steven" image="120" subtitle="CEO" company="Saxton" link="#"]Thank you so much for the great training! For the first time ever I wasn’t nervous going to a customer meeting—I had my plan and knew exactly what I was going to do.[/testimonial][/elements_carousel][vc_empty_space height="50px"][vc_separator color="custom" accent_color="rgba(54,70,115,0